leave his body again?

6
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:58,660
I'm not sure either.

7
00:01:59,789 --> 00:02:01,760
But this time,
there's a golden body shield.

8
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,710
Master's primordial spirit should be safe.

9
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,400
Should be?

10
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,200
When it comes to Master's safety,

11
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,840
how can you speak with such uncertainty?

12
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,910
I'm a healer,

13
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,090
not a soul summoner.

14
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,400
It must be that witch Siling

15
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,000
who used some trick

16
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,190
to steal Master's primordial spirit!

17
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:26,250
We shouldn't have let her stay alive.

18
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:27,490
It might not be her.

19
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:28,880
Then who else,

20
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:31,560
in all 12 provinces of Han,

21
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,300
would want to harm Master?

22
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,079
The Heavenly Lord's primordial spirit
has left his body once more.

23
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,750
Something's definitely happened.

24
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,030
Right now, the most urgent thing

25
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:41,890
is to find out
where his primordial spirit has gone.

26
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,820
I'm going to wipe out
Jingyun Sect right now.

27
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:48,120
Let's see if Siling still dares
to lay a hand on Master!

28
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:50,520
The Heavenly Lord said
we must not harm her.

29
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:54,610
That's only because
Master's been bewitched by her.

30
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:56,470
Protecting Master

31
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:58,280
is our duty as disciples.

32
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:01,000
It's my responsibility
to remove any threat to him.

33
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,870
Let's not even say for sure
whether it was Divine Lord Siling's doing.

34
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:07,470
With your cultivation level,
how could you possibly defeat her?

35
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:10,360
You're right. I can't beat her.

36
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,240
But who said I'm going alone this time?

37
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,400
Come back—

38
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,520
Take good care of the Heavenly Lord.

39
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:25,579
I'll go check on him
before he stirs up any more trouble.

40
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:37,710
Master.

41
